---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'

import CheckboxBadge from '../../components/CheckboxBadge.astro'
import BadgeFilter from '../../components/BadgeFilter.astro'
import ProjectCard from '../../components/ProjectCard.astro'

const cPluPlusTemplateDescription = `
C++ template repository providing a structured, preconfigured foundation for C++ based projects.
It integrates tools for dependency management, linting and formatting, building, testing
along with security analysis, both in own code and third party libraries (based on public databases)
and Github CI/CD workflows.
`

const pythonTemplateDescription = `
Python template repository providing a structured, preconfigured foundation for Python based projects.
It integrates tools for dependency and environment management, linting and formatting, building, testing
along with security analysis, both in own code and third party libraries (based on public databases)
and Github CI/CD workflows.
`

const tiltPlaneDescription = `
Building of a 3D printed tiltrotor airplane, with modular components for easy assembly/disassembly,
integrating an autopilot based on Ardupilot and communications based on
open source ELRS (Express Long Range System).
The airplane structure leverages very lightweight self-foaming ASA and
stronger carbon fiber reinforced PLA for critical components.
`

const infotaxisDescription = `
Development of a search algorithm, to detect and localize the source of a chemical substance
in dilute mediums. Search is accomplished by combining olfactory sensing of the source's chemical marker (using
electronic noses) with mathematical strategy, modeling the substance diffusion process and
information theory to process detected signals. The scope includes the numerical implementation
of the algorithm, and subsequent robustness analyses to account for sensor and parametric model uncertainties.

`

const quadcopterDescription = `
Development of a DIY quadcopter, which included both software and hardware.
Preliminar analysis was performed in a simulator implemented in MATLAB.
Fine tuning of PID gains was done analyzing system's response to several input types.
`

const airshipDescription = `
Final degree project, developed during my internship in Unmanned Solutions (USOL).
The work's scope covers most of a product's lifecycle: conceptual - preliminary - detailed design, and construction of a prototype for testing purposes.
The objective was to analyse the advantages of new airships in comparison with other air vehicles in its interval of range - velocity.
During the conceptual design phase, a numerical model of the airship implemented in Simulink/Matlab was developed to carry out performance analysis and support design decisions.
`

const groundStationDescription = `
Development of a ground station using Qt. The code was programmed in C++/QML.
The purpose of the ground station is to allow the control of autonomous RPAS from a single computer,
monitorizing their actual positions in a 2D displayed map as well as the required aditional parameters
as function of time. Control over the RPAS can be acquired, commanding pre-defined functions
or controlling their movement using a gamepad.
`

const geneticAlgorithmsDescription = `
Application of genetic algorithms to optimize a car’s 2D longitudinal shape for drag reduction.
The geometry is parameterized as segmented exponential functions, whose coefficients are optimized
by the genetic algorithm based on values of the objective function, the drag coefficient.
For each candidate solution, drag is evaluated via CFD in Ansys Fluent.
`

const cheopsDescription = `
The scope of the internship was to developed a high precision Flight Dynamics System (FDS) tool
and use it to analyze CHEOPS mission (ESA satellite) and optimize some design parameters.
The code was implemented in MATLAB, in an user-friendly form through the use of several GUIs,
avoiding the need of modifying internal code. All models are based on recommendations of IERS Conventions 2010 bulletin.
`

const roverDescription = `
Building and programming of a rover vehicle to perform experimental campaigns in real condition scenarios
and validate numerical analyses obtained in Infotaxis project. 3D printing was used for construction
of many parts, and the main controller, based on a STM32 chip, implemented a PID control to follow waypoints.
`
---

<BaseLayout
    body-class="flex flex-col min-h-screen bg-white text-gray-800 dark:bg-gray-900 dark:text-gray-200"
    header-navbar-class="sticky top-0 z-20 w-full flex-none"
>
    <main class="mx-auto flex-1">
        <!-- Filter controls -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-8 py-4 md:py-8 lg:gap-16">
            <!-- Input search -->
            <form class="w-full max-w-md">
                <label for="search" class="sr-only mb-2.5 block text-sm font-medium text-heading"
                    >Search</label
                >
                <div class="relative">
                    <div
                        class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-y-0 inset-s-0 flex items-center ps-3"
                    >
                        <svg
                            class="h-4 w-4 text-body"
                            aria-hidden="true"
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            width="24"
                            height="24"
                            fill="none"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        >
                            <path
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-width="2"
                                d="m21 21-3.5-3.5M17 10a7 7 0 1 1-14 0 7 7 0 0 1 14 0Z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <input
                        type="search"
                        id="search"
                        data-search-target=".card"
                        data-search-scope="#container-project-cards"
                        class="block w-full rounded-base border border-default-medium bg-neutral-secondary-medium p-3 ps-9 text-sm text-heading shadow-xs placeholder:text-body focus:border-brand focus:ring-brand"
                        placeholder="Search"
                    />
                    <button
                        type="submit"
                        class="absolute inset-e-1.5 bottom-1.5 box-border rounded border border-transparent bg-brand px-3 py-1.5 text-xs leading-5 font-medium text-white shadow-xs hover:bg-brand-strong focus:ring-4 focus:ring-brand-medium focus:outline-none"
                    >
                        Search
                    </button>
                </div>
            </form>

            <!-- Filter dropdown -->
            <button
                id="button-filter-tags"
                data-dropdown-toggle="dropdown-filter-tags"
                class="inline-flex items-center space-x-3 rounded-lg bg-blue-700 px-5 py-2.5 text-center text-sm font-medium text-white hover:bg-blue-800 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-300 focus:outline-none dark:bg-blue-600 dark:hover:bg-blue-700 dark:focus:ring-blue-800"
                type="button"
            >
                <svg
                    class="h-4 w-4"
                    aria-hidden="true"
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    width="24"
                    height="24"
                    fill="none"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                    <path
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        d="M18.796 4H5.204a1 1 0 0 0-.753 1.659l5.302 6.058a1 1 0 0 1 .247.659v4.874a.5.5 0 0 0 .2.4l3 2.25a.5.5 0 0 0 .8-.4v-7.124a1 1 0 0 1 .247-.659l5.302-6.059c.566-.646.106-1.658-.753-1.658Z"
                    ></path>
                </svg>

                <span>Filter</span>
                <svg
                    class="h-2.5 w-2.5"
                    aria-hidden="true"
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    fill="none"
                    viewBox="0 0 10 6"
                >
                    <path
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        d="m1 1 4 4 4-4"></path>
                </svg>
            </button>
            <div
                id="dropdown-filter-tags"
                class="z-10 hidden w-48 divide-y divide-gray-100 rounded-lg bg-white shadow dark:divide-gray-600 dark:bg-gray-700"
            >
                <ul
                    id="checkbox-list"
                    class="h-48 space-y-3 overflow-y-auto p-3 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"
                    aria-labelledby="dropdownCheckboxButton"
                >
                    <li>
                        <CheckboxBadge color-scheme="programming-languages" data-tag="Qt" />
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <CheckboxBadge color-scheme="programming-languages" data-tag="MATLAB" />
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <CheckboxBadge color-scheme="programming-languages" data-tag="C++" />
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <CheckboxBadge color-scheme="programming-languages" data-tag="Arduino" />
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <CheckboxBadge color-scheme="programming-languages" data-tag="Python" />
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <CheckboxBadge color-scheme="tech-areas" data-tag="statistics" />
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <CheckboxBadge color-scheme="tech-areas" data-tag="embedded-systems" />
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <CheckboxBadge color-scheme="tech-areas" data-tag="aircraft-design" />
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <CheckboxBadge color-scheme="tech-areas" data-tag="simulation" />
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <CheckboxBadge color-scheme="tech-areas" data-tag="optimization" />
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <CheckboxBadge color-scheme="tech-areas" data-tag="3D-printing" />
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <CheckboxBadge color-scheme="tech-areas" data-tag="orbital-mechanics" />
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <CheckboxBadge color-scheme="tech-areas" data-tag="control" />
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <CheckboxBadge color-scheme="domain-industry" data-tag="agriculture" />
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <CheckboxBadge color-scheme="domain-industry" data-tag="aerospace" />
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <CheckboxBadge
                            color-scheme="scale-collaboration-type"
                            data-tag="personal"
                        />
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <CheckboxBadge
                            color-scheme="scale-collaboration-type"
                            data-tag="professional"
                        />
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <CheckboxBadge color-scheme="skills" data-tag="test" />
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="active-bagdes" class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center py-4 md:py-8">
            <BadgeFilter color-scheme="programming-languages" data-tag="Qt" />
            <BadgeFilter color-scheme="programming-languages" data-tag="MATLAB" />
            <BadgeFilter color-scheme="programming-languages" data-tag="C++" />
            <BadgeFilter color-scheme="programming-languages" data-tag="Arduino" />
            <BadgeFilter color-scheme="programming-languages" data-tag="Python" />
            <BadgeFilter color-scheme="tech-areas" data-tag="statistics" />
            <BadgeFilter color-scheme="tech-areas" data-tag="embedded-systems" />
            <BadgeFilter color-scheme="tech-areas" data-tag="aircraft-design" />
            <BadgeFilter color-scheme="tech-areas" data-tag="simulation" />
            <BadgeFilter color-scheme="tech-areas" data-tag="optimization" />
            <BadgeFilter color-scheme="tech-areas" data-tag="3D-printing" />
            <BadgeFilter color-scheme="tech-areas" data-tag="orbital-mechanics" />
            <BadgeFilter color-scheme="tech-areas" data-tag="control" />
            <BadgeFilter color-scheme="domain-industry" data-tag="agriculture" />
            <BadgeFilter color-scheme="domain-industry" data-tag="aerospace" />
            <BadgeFilter color-scheme="scale-collaboration-type" data-tag="personal" />
            <BadgeFilter color-scheme="scale-collaboration-type" data-tag="professional" />
            <BadgeFilter color-scheme="skills" data-tag="test" />
        </div>
        <div
            id="container-project-cards"
            class="grid grid-cols-1 items-start justify-items-center gap-x-8 gap-y-4 py-8 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-x-16 lg:gap-y-8 lg:px-8 lg:py-16"
        >
            <ProjectCard
                title="C++ Template"
                initial-date="01/2026"
                status="maintained"
                description={cPluPlusTemplateDescription}
                rel-path-project="/projects/none"
                rel-path-image="cpluplus_template"
                color-scheme='["programming-languages"]'
                data-tags='["C++"]'
            />
            <ProjectCard
                title="Python Template"
                initial-date="05/2025"
                status="maintained"
                description={pythonTemplateDescription}
                rel-path-project="/projects/none"
                rel-path-image="python_template"
                color-scheme='["programming-languages"]'
                data-tags='["Python"]'
            />
            <ProjectCard
                title="Tiltplane"
                initial-date="05/2025"
                end-date="08/2025"
                status="completed"
                description={tiltPlaneDescription}
                rel-path-project="/projects/none"
                rel-path-image="tiltplane"
                color-scheme='["programming-languages", "tech-areas", "tech-areas", "tech-areas", "domain-industry"]'
                data-tags='["C++", "embedded-systems", "3D-printing", "electronics", "aerospace"]'
            />
            <ProjectCard
                title="Infotaxis"
                initial-date="11/2015"
                end-date="08/2016"
                status="completed"
                description={infotaxisDescription}
                rel-path-project="/projects/infotaxis"
                rel-path-image="infotaxis"
                color-scheme='["programming-languages", "tech-areas", "tech-areas", "domain-industry"]'
                data-tags='["MATLAB", "statistics", "simulation", "agriculture"]'
            />
            <ProjectCard
                title="Quadcopter DIY"
                initial-date="06/2015"
                end-date="03/2016"
                status="completed"
                description={quadcopterDescription}
                rel-path-project="/projects/none"
                rel-path-image="quadcopter"
                color-scheme='["programming-languages", "programming-languages", "tech-areas", "tech-areas", "domain-industry"]'
                data-tags='["MATLAB", "Arduino", "embedded-systems", "control", "aerospace"]'
            />
            <ProjectCard
                title="Autonomous Airship"
                initial-date="02/2016"
                end-date="10/2016"
                status="completed"
                description={airshipDescription}
                rel-path-project="/projects/none"
                rel-path-image="airship"
                color-scheme='["programming-languages", "programming-languages", "tech-areas", "tech-areas", "tech-areas", "domain-industry"]'
                data-tags='["MATLAB", "Arduino", "aircraft-design", "embedded-systems", "simulation", "aerospace"]'
            />
            <ProjectCard
                title="Ground Station"
                initial-date="11/2016"
                end-date="08/2017"
                status="completed"
                description={groundStationDescription}
                rel-path-project="/projects/none"
                rel-path-image="ground_station"
                color-scheme='["programming-languages", "programming-languages", "tech-areas", "tech-areas", "domain-industry"]'
                data-tags='["Qt", "C++", "front-end", "MAVLink", "comms"]'
            />
            <ProjectCard
                title="Genetic Algorithms"
                initial-date="09/2016"
                end-date="12/2016"
                status="completed"
                description={geneticAlgorithmsDescription}
                rel-path-project="/projects/none"
                rel-path-image="optimization"
                color-scheme='["programming-languages", "tech-areas"]'
                data-tags='["MATLAB", "optimization"]'
            />
            <ProjectCard
                title="CHEOPS"
                initial-date="03/2018"
                end-date="03/2019"
                status="completed"
                description={cheopsDescription}
                rel-path-project="/projects/none"
                rel-path-image="cheops"
                color-scheme='["programming-languages", "tech-areas", "tech-areas", "domain-industry"]'
                data-tags='["MATLAB", "numerical-calculus", "orbital-mechanics", "aerospace"]'
            />
            <ProjectCard
                title="Rover"
                initial-date="01/2018"
                end-date="01/2022"
                status="completed"
                description={roverDescription}
                rel-path-project="/projects/none"
                rel-path-image="rover"
                color-scheme='["programming-languages", "tech-areas", "tech-areas"]'
                data-tags='["Arduino", "3D-printing", "electronics"]'
            />
        </div>
    </main>

    <script src="/src/scripts/projects.js"></script>
</BaseLayout>
